---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const HOPITUDE_URL = 'https://app.hopitude.com/en/calendar?cl=2376';
---

<Layout
  title="Book a Session – Breathwork & Floating | Hingamiskeskus"
  description="Book a session for breathwork or floating at Hingamiskeskus in Tallinn. Release tension, find inner balance and experience deep relaxation. Book your session today!"
  keywords="Broneeri-aeg, Teadlik vabastav hingamine, book a session"
  lang="en"
  alternates={{ et: '/broneeri-aeg', ru: '/ru/zabronirovat-vremya', en: '/en/book-a-session' }}
>

<Header active="broneeri" lang="en" />

<section class="booking">
  <h1 class="booking__title">Floating and breathwork sessions, book a session</h1>

  <h2>How to book?</h2>
  <p>1. Choose a suitable time and service from the calendar</p>
  <p>2. Create an account in our booking system</p>
  <p>3. Choose a payment method, pay by online bank or in cash on site</p>
  <p>After confirming your booking, we will send a confirmation to your email.</p>

  <div class="booking__calendar">
    <iframe
      src={HOPITUDE_URL}
      title="Booking calendar"
      loading="lazy"
      frameborder="0"
    ></iframe>
  </div>

  <h2>Book a session for breathwork or floating in Tallinn</h2>
  <p>Hingamiskeskus offers breathwork and floating. Our experienced therapists guide you safely throughout the whole process, whether you come for the first time or are already a regular visitor. Hingamiskeskus is the only place in Tallinn where you can experience breathwork in warm water.</p>
  <p><a href="/en/breathwork">Breathwork</a> helps release emotional and physical tension, relieve stress and anxiety, and achieve inner clarity. The session lasts 2 hours and takes place in a private and calm room.</p>
  <p><a href="/en/floating">Floating</a>, floating in Epsom salt water, relaxes the muscles, calms the nervous system and improves sleep. One hour of floating gives the body the same deep rest as 4 hours of sleep.</p>
  <p>All sessions take place at Hingamiskeskus near the center of Tallinn at Sõle 14c. Parking is available in front of the building and on Mulla street.</p>

  <h2>What happens after booking?</h2>
  <p>After booking, we will send a confirmation to your email along with practical instructions. Please arrive 15 minutes before the session begins. On your first visit, the therapist will introduce the service and answer all your questions.</p>
  <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us, we are always happy to help!</p>

  <a href={HOPITUDE_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="booking__btn">BOOK A SESSION</a>
</section>

<Footer lang="en" />

</Layout>

<style>
  .booking {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 24px 60px;
    background: #f3fcff;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .booking { padding: 60px 40px 80px; }
  }

  .booking__title {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1d1e20;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .booking__title { font-size: 42px; }
  }

  .booking h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1d1e20;
    text-align: left;
    margin: 32px 0 14px;
  }

  .booking p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .booking a { color: #1f6d85; text-decoration: underline; }

  .booking__calendar {
    margin: 28px 0 8px;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(31, 109, 133, 0.08);
  }
  .booking__calendar iframe {
    width: 100%;
    height: 680px;
    display: block;
    border: 0;
  }

  .booking__btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #1d1e20;
    color: #fff !important;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .booking__btn:hover { opacity: 0.88; }

  .location {
    background: #1f6d85;
    padding: 20px 24px 24px;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .location__title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .location__address { font-size: 14px; }
  .location__photo { width: 80%; max-width: 320px; margin: 12px auto 0; display: block; border-radius: 10px; }
  .footer__main { background: #1f6d85; padding: 24px; color: #fff; }
  .footer__logo { height: 30px; width: auto; margin: 0 auto 20px; display: block; }
  .footer__contact h3, .footer__hours h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .footer__contact p, .footer__hours p { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8; }
  .footer__hours { margin-top: 16px; }
  .footer__social { display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-top: 16px; color: #fff; }
  .footer__legal { font-size: 11px; margin-top: 16px; opacity: 0.7; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding-top: 12px; }
  .footer__legal a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }
</style>
